cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with generating natural language descriptions of images. It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) because it involves processing and analyzing visual data. Additionally, it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it involves training networks to perform a joint task. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it involves developing algorithms that can communicate and cooperate to achieve a goal. Finally, it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because it involves generating descriptions that can be used to retrieve relevant images.
